sequenceDiagram
    participant YML as Genre Pack YAML
    participant LS as LoreStore (in-memory)
    participant API as HTTP API
    participant NAR as Narrator Agent

    YML->>LS: Load entries at server startup
    note over LS: Indexed by category + keywords

    NAR->>API: GET /lore/category/factions
    API->>LS: query_by_category("factions")
    LS-->>API: [LoreEntry, LoreEntry, ...]
    API-->>NAR: JSON array

    NAR->>API: GET /lore/search?q=iron
    API->>LS: query_by_keyword("iron")
    LS-->>API: [matching LoreEntry, ...]
    API-->>NAR: JSON array

    NAR->>NAR: Build scene context with lore